commit.message: Re-generate "configure". This should remove the version number from the stub library name, when compiling for Tcl 9
Allow library commands to work with Tk 9.
Fix compile and link issue found in pkgs environment
In case other extensions didn't upgrade rules.vc/tcl.m4, make it still possible to use "itcl.h"
Build "Tcl_Size" definition into rules.vc/configure, in stead of itcl header-files
Remove a few unneeded shadowed variables
Fix [https://core.tcl-lang.org/tclconfig/info/c981aa093a|c981aa093a]: PKG_STUB_LIB_FILE wrong for Windows. Update TEA
Adapt Itcl to TIP #673: Remove deprecated [trace] subcommands
Update TEA for itclWidget as well
Adapt release notes. Some more pre-release tweaks
More Tcl 9 adaptations (was not finished - after all)
More usage of Tcl_Size, in stead of #if's
Remove unnecessary type-casts. Handle isNativeObjectProc == 2 better
Don't compile Itcl with -DTCL_NO_DEPRECATED any more
